Death Benefit:
Death Benefit = SA from Risk Cover Schedule decreasing yearly as per chosen interest rate (6–12%).  
Limited PPT: higher of 105% premiums or Schedule SA.  
Single PPT: Schedule SA only. :contentReference[oaicite:12]{index=12}

